    <h1>What is Pet Handler</h1>
    <p>Pet Handler is a company that helps animals, we rescue animals in need. Animals that are neglected from their homes, animals living on the streets. 
        We believe that animals who have raised to be domestic shouldnt be raised to be neglected. They should have love and support from their owners.
