        walk past them not even giving them a second look. We see the mothers or the fathers of the animals struggling to protect their little babies or 
        provding food to feed them. We see sick animals or even dying aniamls all over Auckland yet no one tried to help them. This we why we created this 
        company. We provide safe homes for the aniamls. We treat them, feed them, bathe them until they either recover or we find them new homes. We create
        safe enviroment for the animals until we find them safe and permanemt homes for them. If we find them in families we try to find homes who we take 
